I'm initiating an immediate rotation of all secrets associated with that CI/CD pipeline and locking down the Azure subscription level permissions. I don't care if it breaks the current deployment—we're already in a state of drift, and I'm not letting them deepen their persistence. 

@Elena Rodriguez, I need SecOps to pull the audit logs for that SP immediately. Who created it, and what have they touched since it was provisioned? I'm going to isolate the CI/CD runners until we can verify the integrity of the templates. My head is killing me, but I'm on it.

