Dane, I need a concise summary of exactly what infrastructure assets were touched by that Service Principal. I am drafting our preliminary materiality assessment for the board and SEC. We need to move fast.

@all Regarding the unauthorized modification of our ARM templates and the potential compromise of the model training environment: 

