I need an immediate, granular audit trail of exactly what data, if any, was accessed via that Service Principal. If those credentials touched the DoW-segregated environments, we are looking at a mandatory breach notification window that is significantly shorter than standard commercial disclosures. 

Do not communicate with any external parties, including the Department of War, until I have reviewed the draft of the disclosure. Any premature admission of liability without a full forensic understanding of the exfiltration scope will be catastrophic for our standing. 

