Sarah, we must prepare for an immediate 8-K filing. We cannot rely on internal remediation to mitigate the materiality of this breach. The unauthorized access to our model training environment, coupled with the Department of War contract exposure, constitutes a reportable event of the highest order. Dane, provide me with a forensic timeline of the Service Principal's activity for the inevitable regulatory audit. We are now in a defensive posture against both the adversary and the federal government.

